function generateProgressBar(current, target) {
  const percentage = Math.min(Math.round((current / target) * 100), 100);
  const filledBars = Math.round(percentage / 10);
  const emptyBars = 10 - filledBars;
  
  let bar = "‚ñì".repeat(filledBars) + "‚ñë".repeat(emptyBars);
  let status = "";
  
  if (percentage < 30) status = "üî¥ Baixo";
  else if (percentage < 70) status = "üü° M√©dio";
  else if (percentage < 90) status = "üü¢ Bom";
  else if (percentage <= 110) status = "‚úÖ Ideal";
  else status = "üîµ Acima";
  
  return `[${bar}] ${status}`;
}
